    </div>
    <a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/smj.2575" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="link text-sm">Read the paper ↗</a>
  </article>

  <article class="mb-12">
    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Entrepreneurial Strategies During Institutional Changes: Evidence from China's Economic Transition</h3>
    <p class="text-base mb-4">
      What China's regional economic transition tells us about which entrepreneurial strategies pay off when institutions shift. <em>Strategic Entrepreneurship Journal</em>, 2022 (with You (Willow) Wu and Delin Yang).
    </p>
    <div class="aspect-video mb-3 border border-base-300 rounded overflow-hidden">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/NXQUYyQdY1U"
